---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="About Me | Attachment Matters, LLC" 
    description="Learn about my experience, credentials, and therapeutic approach. I am a relationship-driven, attachment-focused, and trauma-responsive clinician.">
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-deep-purple text-center">My Philosophy & Approach</h1>
            
            <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="md:col-span-2">
                    <!-- IMPORTANT: Replace this src with the path to your actual headshot image -->
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x400.png/f4d3d3/483248?text=Your+Headshot" alt="Headshot of the therapist" class="rounded-full shadow-2xl mx-auto w-64 h-64 md:w-full md:h-auto object-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-3">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-rust">Warm, Compassionate, and Highly Skilled</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
                        The most critical thing you should know is that I am a client-centered provider who is exceptionally skilled at what I do. With **16 years of experience** in complex family systems, I have earned a reputation as a leading professional in the region. 
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
                        As an LCSW for 14 years with a spotless ethical record, my approach is always relationship-driven, attachment-focused, and trauma-responsive.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-20 bg-white/70 p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-deep-purple text-center">My Therapeutic Toolbox</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-light text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    I use an eclectic, integrative style, drawing from a wide array of evidence-based practices to support your family's unique journey to bonding and wellness.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
                    <span class="bg-brand-deep-purple text-white/90 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Cognitive Behavior Therapy (CBT)</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-deep-purple text-white/90 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Child Centered Play Therapy</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-deep-purple text-white/90 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Synergetic Play Therapy (SPT)</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-deep-purple text-white/90 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Parent Child Interactional Therapy (PCIT)</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-deep-purple text-white/90 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">The Neurosequential Model</span>
                    <span class="bg-brand-deep-purple text-white/90 font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-full">Trauma Focused CBT (TF-CBT)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>